                        Elevate Your<br>
                        <span class="text-blue-800">K-12 Learning Journey</span>
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
                        Experience excellence in education with our comprehensive K-12 program designed to nurture young minds and create future leaders.
                    </p>
                    <button class="bg-blue-800 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-900 transition-colors">
                        Learn More
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- WhatsApp Button -->
    <a href="https://wa.me/916307995251" 
       class="fixed bottom-6 right-6 bg-green-500 text-white p-4 rounded-full shadow-lg hover:bg-green-600 transition-colors z-40"
       target="_blank"
       rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <i class='bx bxl-whatsapp text-2xl'></i>
    </a>

    <script>
        function closeModal() {
            document.getElementById('admissionModal').style.display = 'none';
        }
